title: Fresh peach upside down cake
ingredients: ['50g butter', '110g light brown soft sugar', '1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '5 fresh peaches - peeled, stones removed and halved', '110g butter, softened', '100g caster sugar', '1 egg', '150g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '120ml milk']
